{
  "stem": "19895.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Around Budapest, that forced labor period when-- when we were involved in that for about a week or 10 days, or so-- can't remember the exact number of days-- it was organized and very, very disorganized.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because food was occasionally given, but delivery of food for that many people digging trenches and how to reach them and so forth was not-- not done like a well organized military outfit.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So even so, if you were under some degree of some authority and-- and organized people who demanded the work from us, it was never thought out how they feed us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Occasionally some food arrived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were trying to-- to offer above the going price around anywhere where they could get contact with some Gentile people or-- on the towns, or around the suburbs of the city.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how we survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also, when families from the city of Budapest found out from some Gentile people who were willing to deliver some-- some news about our whereabouts, sometime they arrived with some packages of food.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there were trickling food in somehow that we-- we-- we didn't starve to death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we sure were very malnourished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And another thing which I like to mention-- during the death march, when my father returned with Wallenberg's papers, from the location where we were separated, a day later or two days later, a person, a Gentile, a neighbor from the same building as the Jewish people lived, and interestingly, during while we were there, I knew that he is a very active Arrow Cross party advocate.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he had a-- a tailor shop.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
